&lt;h2&gt;Requirements&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;UNIX/Linux/Windows/Nginx host&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;PHP 5.2+&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Apache - See below for modules used&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;No MySQL, No Database needed
		&lt;ul&gt;
			&lt;li&gt;UNIX/Linux/Windows/Nginx host&lt;/li&gt;
			&lt;li&gt;PHP 5.2+&lt;/li&gt;
			&lt;li&gt;Apache - See below for modules used&lt;/li&gt;
			&lt;li&gt;No MySQL, No Database needed&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Installation&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Download &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.omind.org/download/&quot;&gt;the latest version of Omind&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Extract the contents of the Zip File&amp;nbsp;to your server.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Navigate to the admin subdirectory, e.g www.domain.com/admin.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Go to &lt;strong&gt;Settings&lt;/strong&gt; pannel and modify Website URL to your own domian.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Done.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Download, extract and upload any language file if you want a non-English installation. The decompressed language file should be put in the /admin/lang folder of the installation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
